sections.text:
53-103.48.Farmers market, defined.

Farmers market means any common facility or area where producers or growers gather on a regular, recurring basis to sell fruits, vegetables, meats, and other farm products directly to consumers.

SourceLaws 2021, LB274, ยง 3.
